@startuml
title Ticket Management System - Ticket Status Lifecycle

[*] --> Draft
Draft --> New : Submit
New --> Assigned : Auto/manual assignment
Assigned --> InProgress : Agent starts work
InProgress --> PendingRequester : Need requester info
InProgress --> PendingVendor : Need vendor support
InProgress --> Escalated : Need specialist

PendingRequester --> InProgress : Requester replies
PendingVendor --> InProgress : Vendor replies
Escalated --> InProgress : Specialist accepts

InProgress --> Resolved : Solution provided
Resolved --> Closed : Requester accepts
Resolved --> Reopened : Requester rejects

Reopened --> InProgress : Reassign owner
Closed --> [*]

New --> Cancelled : Duplicate or invalid
Assigned --> Cancelled : Cancel request
Cancelled --> [*]

@enduml
